{"tid":1394852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[全數贊助5 位有心人] First Aid 真係好重要!!!","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T18:57:01.000Z","uid":296408,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"595cef2b859e00c461503f70f9b505cd9810581f","tid":1394852,"uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>First Aid 真係好好好重要! </strong><br />\n<br />\n就算有冇衝突有冇抗爭, 日常生活裡一定有機會遇到突發事故, 唔想手甩甩唔知點做既話係時候報First Aid 課程啦! <br />\n<br />\n因為我自己真係好驚有一日有需要人士需要人幫手時我自己咩都唔識做, 避免呢個清況發生, 我同男友岩岩己報紅十字會First Aid 課程, 希望有需要時可以有能力為大家出一分力. 其實不嬲都想去學, 只係冇去實行, 雖然而家係遲左d. 但報左總好過唔報. 以下一d 資料俾大家參考, 希望更多人加入救援行列, 當然無論你係義士定唔係義士, 識多一樣重要野旁生都好, 起碼幫到有需要人士, 他朝一日總會用得著唔洗得個望字! <br />\n<br />\n我知道呢度有好多學生或剛畢業同學, 無錢or 儲緊錢買物資 or 開飯都有困難, <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我願意全數贊助 5 位 有心人 or 有需要人士 報名</span>, <br />\n<br />\n條件 係需要俾我知道你有參與 2 次或以上 遊行 or 屬前線人士. 由於我係連登P 牌, 仲未好識用, 有趣既人請留言or pm (唔知呢度有冇pm) .<br />\n<br />\n(why 紅十字會? 因為我其實都係一個上網白痴, 其他地方我唔係好搵到有得學, 紅十字會比較簡潔易明, 當然都歡迎你搵到其他既話又想去既報名) <br />\n<br />\n紅十字會急救証書課程:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctesBhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctesBhr.png&h=e6624d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NuP8kKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNuP8kKg.png&h=04e6ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://training.redcross.org.hk/tms/zh-HK/fatCourseDetails.jspx?courseCode=SFA&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI-pOH1urh4wIVQ3RgCh0m-wrOEAAYASABEgJfPvD_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftraining.redcross.org.hk%2Ftms%2Fzh-HK%2FfatCourseDetails.jspx%3FcourseCode%3DSFA%26gclid%3DEAIaIQobChMI-pOH1urh4wIVQ3RgCh0m-wrOEAAYASABEgJfPvD_BwE&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8a928b73\" target=\"_blank\">https://training.redcross.org.hk/tms/zh-HK/fatCourseDetails.jspx?courseCode=SFA&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI-pOH1urh4wIVQ3RgCh0m-wrOEAAYASABEgJfPvD_BwE</a>"},{"pid":"38a05fdd55a3739ce20169c4ac72f377ffc89de1","tid":1394852,"uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ec3fbbfaef2ca7b9b4b7dd2c68e347b985dba530","tid":1394852,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"有少少興趣 但係夜晚要反pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36f0dcd6a0c8e5c408ce22c83ad669e4c7679e6","tid":1394852,"uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3fbbfaef2ca7b9b4b7dd2c68e347b985dba530","tid":1394852,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"有少少興趣 但係夜晚要反pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"晏奏呢? 佢都有d 係星期六日, 平日都有..."},{"pid":"d5ca7b379200d6993c7e431434acd1d149e9cec8","tid":1394852,"uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"再自推! 絲打們出力既時候!!!"},{"pid":"864a8dc9be886c09eca4f168e5c30e7668b5f3f4","tid":1394852,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d36f0dcd6a0c8e5c408ce22c83ad669e4c7679e6","tid":1394852,"uid":296408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3fbbfaef2ca7b9b4b7dd2c68e347b985dba530","tid":1394852,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"有少少興趣 但係夜晚要反pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"晏奏呢? 佢都有d 係星期六日, 平日都有..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"星期六日就要出黎發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29874f9554d0511d6304b23a12bdf7e1b92d622e","tid":1394852,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"條件 係需要俾我知道你有參與 2 次或以上 遊行 or 屬前線人士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/