 無錢or 儲緊錢買物資 or 開飯都有困難, <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我願意全數贊助 5 位 有心人 or 有需要人士 報名</span>, <br />\n<br />\n條件 係需要俾我知道你有參與 2 次或以上 遊行 or 屬前線人士. 由於我係連登P 牌, 仲未好識用, 有趣既人請留言or pm (唔知呢度有冇pm) .<br />\n<br />\n(why 紅十字會? 因為我其實都係一個上網白痴, 其他地方我唔係好搵到有得學, 紅十字會比較簡潔易明, 當然都歡迎你搵到其他既話又想去既報名) <br />\n<br />\n紅十字會急救証書課程:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctesBhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctesBhr.png&h=e6624d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NuP8kKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNuP8kKg.png&h=04e6ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://training.redcross.org.hk/tms/zh-HK/fatCourseDetails.jspx?courseCode=SFA&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI-pOH1urh4wIVQ3RgCh0m-wrOEAAYASABEgJfPvD_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftraining.redcross.org.hk%2Ftms%2Fzh-HK%2FfatCourseDetails.jspx%3FcourseCode%3DSFA%26gclid%3DEAIaIQobChMI-pOH1urh4wIVQ3RgCh0m-wrOEAAYASABEgJfPvD_BwE&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8a928b73\" target=\"_blank\">https://training.redcross.org.hk/tms/zh-HK/fatCourseDetails.jspx?courseCode=SFA&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI-pOH1urh4wIVQ3RgCh0m-wrOEAAYASABEgJfPvD_BwE</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"幫推 我都可以sponsor 5個    唔洗發過夢 tg me  <a href=\"https://t.me/Dinneronme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDinneronme&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=69330b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dinneronme</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20ec31ef6aec731590e7d0d2305f1fda3ca26e3","tid":1394852,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b800d95b4922be950dfdac434b3d861